{
  "workflow": {
    "id": 13764,
    "name": "Notify new BOAMP IT tenders to a Slack channel with the BOAMP API",
    "views": 2,
    "recentViews": 0,
    "totalViews": 2,
    "createdAt": "2026-02-28T01:57:30.695Z",
    "description": "## How it works\n\n• Config node for channel, keyword, limit, and empty-results message\n• Fetches tenders from BOAMP API (public data, no API key)\n• Formats message with title, date, buyer, link - or sends friendly \"no results\" message\n• Posts to your Slack channel\n\n## Set up steps\n\n• Add Slack credential - ~2 min\n• Edit Config node (channel, keyword, limit, EMPTY_MESSAGE)\n• Activate the workflow",
    "workflow": {
      "id": "ujc2wJpEj35OK72q",
      "meta": {
        "instanceId": "4fb03e8a794c9a4ffa717f54989f44bb958e64f57e605ef61bad499ca54d20f3",
        "templateCredsSetupCompleted": true
      },
      "name": "Notify new BOAMP IT tenders to Slack channel",
      "tags": [],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "fa25f63e-3a39-4760-a7e5-1f13fd44cdf6",
          "name": "Overview",
          "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
          "position": [
            1232,
            544
          ],
          "parameters": {
            "color": 5,
            "width": 500,
            "height": 380,
            "content": "## BOAMP to Slack Notification\n\n**Who it's for:** Consultants, ESN, and agencies who want instant Slack alerts when new IT tenders are published on the French BOAMP platform.\n\n**What it does:** Runs on schedule (every 6h) or manually, fetches tenders from BOAMP, formats a readable message, and posts to Slack. Configurable keyword, limit, and channel. Sends a friendly message when no tenders are found.\n\n**Setup:** Add Slack credential. Adjust Config node (channel, keyword, limit)."
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "0cae8cd7-20ca-4cdf-81e8-dc5cda58e9bd",
          "name": "Sticky Note 1",
          "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
          "position": [
            1776,
            576
          ],
          "parameters": {
            "color": 7,
            "width": 200,
            "height": 100,
            "content": "**Step 1 - Config**\n\nEdit channel, keyword, limit"
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
        },
